latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Purple A11y is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/purple-a11y-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Bug fixes
- Add custom scan label to Custom Flow 2.0 scans
- Only redirected pages from same domain or hostname should be scanned
- Custom Flow 2.0 bar may not appear on all sites
- Browser crash when sitemap scan in headless mode
- Randomly inaccurate page scan count
- Navigation of category dropdown in report for Android TalkBack users
